          "_name": "article01",
          "_sourceTheme": "discretem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article1\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\n        <input type=\"range\" inline name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n        <select title=\"Align\" name=\"contentAlign\">\n            <option value selected>Left</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-center\">Center</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-end\">Right</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#fafaf9\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#fafafa\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.1\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div class mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row  align-left {{contentAlign}}\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"align-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showSubitle\">\n                    <div class=\"subtitle-wrap\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-idea mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle, .align-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubitle\"><b>Process</b></h2>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>How to Manage <br>Your Business</b></h1>\n\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">The company provides a wide range of construction services designed to enhance both the functionality and appearance of residential and commercial properties. Its expertise includes demolition, interior and exterior remodeling, and improvements to key living areas such as kitchens, bathrooms, and basements. ORA Construction also specializes in building extensions and dormers that expand usable space and improve the overall value of a property. In addition, the company undertakes concrete work such as sidewalks and driveways, along with large-scale construction projects that involve building new homes from the initial layout through the final finishing stages.<br>\n<br>What sets ORA Construction apart is its commitment to delivering projects that reflect both durability and thoughtful design. Every project is approached with careful planning and close collaboration with clients to ensure their vision is accurately translated into a finished result. By combining industry knowledge with reliable construction practices, the company is able to manage projects from concept to completion while maintaining high standards of quality and safety.<br>\n<br>As a fully licensed and insured contractor, ORA Construction prioritizes professionalism and accountability in every aspect of its work. Clients rely on the company not only for its technical expertise but also for its transparent communication and dedication to meeting project timelines. Through years of hands-on experience and a strong focus on craftsmanship, ORA Construction continues to help property owners transform their spaces into functional, well-built environments designed to stand the test of time.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Create\n                        Website</a></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
