          "_name": "article02",
          "_sourceTheme": "launchm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article02 launchm5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow 1\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"cardShadow_1\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow 2\" value=\"#cccccc\" name=\"cardShadow_2\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Container BG\" value=\"#fafafa\" name=\"cardBg\">\n        <header>Border</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Border\" name=\"showBorder\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#e1e7ed\" name=\"border\" condition=\"showBorder\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/launchm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f5f5f5\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/launchm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#f5f5f5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"border-wrap border_1\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"border-wrap border_2\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                        <div class=\"row items-wrapper\">\n                            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 card\">\n                                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Integrating Concrete Into Larger Home Construction Projects</b></h2>\n                                    <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrapper\">Concrete isn’t limited to driveways and sidewalks. In fact, it plays a vital role in many broader residential construction projects.<br>\n<br>During <a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/6NezeWWMJngRik7C7\" class=\"text-primary\"><u>new home construction Long Island</u></a> developments, concrete forms the backbone of foundations, walkways, garages, and outdoor living areas. Its structural strength ensures the entire property has a stable base.<br>\n<br>Concrete also complements renovation work. A home addition contractor Long Island homeowners rely on may extend driveways or create new pathways that connect expanded living spaces. These additions require materials that match the durability of the existing structure.<br>\n<br>The same principle applies to interior renovations. For example, when undertaking a basement remodel Long Island residents often incorporate concrete flooring or reinforced structures that improve both stability and moisture resistance.<br>\n<br>Because of its versatility, concrete remains a cornerstone material for builders seeking long-lasting results.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Get Started\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 card\">\n                                <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                                    <img class=\"little-radius\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/23.webp\" alt>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "venLhBHYdG",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "article02-1h"
        },
        {
          "_name": "tabs01",
          "_sourceTheme": "standm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"tabs01 tabs standm5\" group=\"List\" plugins=\"mbr-tabs\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Tabs</header>\n        <select title=\"Count\" name=\"bootstrapTabs\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"4\" selected>4</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"tabs\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG\" value=\"#000000\" name=\"tabsBg\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Active Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"activeColor\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Active BG\" value=\"#e70000\" name=\"activeBg\" selected>\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Date\" name=\"showDate\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG 1\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"cardBg_1\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG 2\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" name=\"cardBg_2\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow\" value=\"#6c7179\" name=\"shadow\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/standm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/standm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12\">\n                            <div class=\"tabs-wrapper\">\n                                <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\" role=\"tablist\">\n                                    <li mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"nav-item first mbr-fonts-style\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd,-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-iconFont\"><a class=\"nav-link show mbr-fonts-style little-radius active\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tabs01-5_tab0\" aria-selected=\"true\">\n                                            310 Harbor Rd, Cold Spring Harbor, NY 11724, USA\n                                        </a></li>\n                                    <li mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"nav-item\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 1\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd,-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-iconFont\"><a class=\"nav-link mbr-fonts-style little-radius active\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tabs01-5_tab1\" aria-selected=\"true\">\n                                            2500 6th St, East Meadow, NY 11554, USA\n                                        </a></li>\n                                    <li mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"nav-item\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 2\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd,-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-iconFont\"><a class=\"nav-link mbr-fonts-style little-radius active\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tabs01-5_tab2\" aria-selected=\"true\">\n                                            1135 Walt Whitman Rd, Melville, NY 11747, USA\n                                        </a></li>\n                                    <li mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"nav-item\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 3\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd,-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-iconFont\"><a class=\"nav-link mbr-fonts-style little-radius active\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tabs01-5_tab3\" aria-selected=\"true\">\n                                            8 Woodhollow Ln, Huntington, NY 11743, USA\n                                        </a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"tab-content\">\n                                <div id=\"tab1\" class=\"tab-pane in active\" role=\"tabpanel\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-wrapper large-radius\">\n                                        <div class=\"card-box card-wrap\">\n                                            <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .tabs-wrapper, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"></h4>\n                                            <p class=\"item-date mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-date\" mbr-if=\"showDate\">\n                                                March 12, 2030\n                                            </p>\n                                            <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\"></p>\n                                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-iconFont\">\n                                                <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    See More\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                                            <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1P1gqkrjFVFunGV4oklU6nsBdTIJSqzA&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div id=\"tab2\" class=\"tab-pane\" role=\"tabpanel\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 1\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-wrapper large-radius\">\n                                        <div class=\"card-box card-wrap\">\n                                            <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .tabs-wrapper, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"></h4>\n                                            <p class=\"item-date mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-date\" mbr-if=\"showDate\">\n                                                June 20, 2030\n                                            </p>\n                                            <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\"></p>\n                                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-iconFont\">\n                                                <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    See More\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                                            <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1voJ75HQHMONUPVPGUWGny8ruYljLVyM&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div id=\"tab3\" class=\"tab-pane\" role=\"tabpanel\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 2\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-wrapper large-radius\">\n                                        <div class=\"card-box card-wrap\">\n                                            <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .tabs-wrapper, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"></h4>\n                                            <p class=\"item-date mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-date\" mbr-if=\"showDate\">\n                                                September 5, 2030\n                                            </p>\n                                            <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\"></p>\n                                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-iconFont\">\n                                                <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    See More\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                                            <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=152Mfe7T5dcVkRr3SypEGl2Tr7zda5dg&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div id=\"tab4\" class=\"tab-pane\" role=\"tabpanel\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 3\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-wrapper large-radius\">\n                                        <div class=\"card-box card-wrap\">\n                                            <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .tabs-wrapper, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">500 Searingtown Rd, Roslyn, NY 11576, USA</h4>\n                                            <p class=\"item-date mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-date\" mbr-if=\"showDate\">\n                                                December 3, 2030\n                                            </p>\n                                            <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1C4jHvOnIbmM-uxI4MNV1XYXa_nqaqaw&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe></p>\n                                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-iconFont\">\n                                                <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    See More\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                                            <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1w19kpBDC2pgpWbHuXjA1dCHc1QwNZI4&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".tabs-wrapper": {
              "margin-bottom": "40px",
              ".nav.nav-tabs": {
                "border": "none",
                "padding": "0",
                "border-radius": "0 !important",
                "background-color": "transparent",
                "display": "inline-flex",
                "flex-wrap": "wrap",
                "gap": "12px",
                ".nav-item": {
                  "padding": "0",
                  "border": "none",
                  "display": "block",
                  "margin": "0",
                  ".nav-link": {
                    "position": "relative",
                    "display": "flex",
                    "align-items": "center",
                    "justify-content": "center",
                    "color": "@tabs",
                    "padding": "17px 24px",
                    "background-color": "@tabsBg",
                    "border": "none",
                    "transition": "background-color 1s ease-in-out",
                    "z-index": "1",
                    "overflow": "hidden",
                    "&::after": {
                      "content": "''",
                      "width": "12px",
                      "height": "12px",
                      "border-radius": "100%",
                      "transition": "all .8s ease",
                      "z-index": "-1",
                      "transform": "scale(1)",
                      "background-color": "@activeBg",
                      "margin-left": "16px",
                      "pointer-events": "none"
                    },
                    "&::before": {
                      "content": "''",
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "right": "24px",
                      "width": "12px",
                      "height": "12px",
                      "border-radius": "100%",
                      "transition": "all .8s ease",
                      "z-index": "1",
                      "opacity": "0",
                      "pointer-events": "none",
                      "background-color": "@activeColor"
                    },
                    "&:hover": {
                      "&::after": {
                        "transform": "scale(1.3)"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  ".nav-link.active": {
                    "color": "@activeColor",
                    "background-color": "@activeBg",
                    "&::after": {
                      "transform": "scale(50)"
                    },
                    "&::before": {
                      "opacity": "1"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".tab-content": {
              ".tab-pane": {
                ".card-wrapper": {
                  "display": "grid",
                  "grid-template-columns": "1fr 1fr",
                  "gap": "8px",
                  "background-color": "@cardBg_1",
                  "padding": "8px",
                  "box-shadow": "0 10px 25px -20px @shadow",
                  "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                    "grid-template-columns": "1fr"
                  },
                  ".card-box": {
                    "padding": "24px",
                    "background-color": "@cardBg_2",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "padding": "20px"
                    },
                    ".item-title": {
                      "margin-bottom": "12px"
                    },
                    ".item-date": {
                      "margin-bottom": "20px"
                    },
                    ".item-text": {
                      "margin-bottom": "0"
                    },
                    ".mbr-section-btn": {
                      "margin-top": "12px",
                      ".btn": {
                        "margin-bottom": "0"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  ".image-wrap": {
                    "position": "relative",
                    "min-height": "420px",
                    "height": "100%",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "height": "300px",
                      "min-height": "auto"
                    },
                    "img": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "top": "0",
                      "left": "0",
                      "width": "100%",
                      "height": "100%",
                      "object-fit": "cover"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".item-title": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".item-date": {
              "color": "#454545"
            },
            ".item-text": {
              "color": "#6c7179"
            }
          },
          "_PHPplaceholders": [],
          "_JSplaceholders": [],
          "_cid": "venLhC9XwJ",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "tabs01-1i"
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "background": "white",
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "width": "fit-content",
              "border-radius": "2rem",
              "padding": "5px 1rem",
              "text-align": "left"
            },
            ".subtitle-wrap": {
              "display": "inline-flex",
              "border-radius": "2rem",
              "padding": "0.5rem",
              "padding-bottom": "0",
              "background": "@primaryColor",
              "flex-direction": "row",
              "width": "fit-content",
              "align-items": "center",
              "margin-bottom": "2rem",
              ".mbr-iconfont": {
                "padding": "0 15px",
                "padding-bottom": "8px",
                "margin": "0",
                "color": "@secondaryColor",
                "font-size": "1.5rem"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#04492e"
            },
            ".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle, .align-wrapper": {
              "color": "#04492e",
              "text-align": "center"
            }
          },
          "_name": "article01",
          "_sourceTheme": "discretem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article1\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\n        <input type=\"range\" inline name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"9\" step=\"1\">\n        <select title=\"Align\" name=\"contentAlign\">\n            <option value selected>Left</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-center\">Center</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-end\">Right</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#fafaf9\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#fafafa\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.1\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div class mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row  align-left {{contentAlign}}\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"align-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showSubitle\">\n                    <div class=\"subtitle-wrap\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-idea mobi-mbri\" style=\"color: rgb(240, 48, 74); fill: rgb(240, 48, 74);\"></span>\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle, .align-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubitle\"><b>The Role Of Skilled Builders In Concrete Longevity</b></h2>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>How to Manage <br>Your Business</b></h1>\n\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Even the best materials depend on skilled craftsmanship. Concrete installation requires precise timing, proper curing, and careful finishing techniques that only experienced professionals can deliver.<br>\n<br>A qualified construction company masonry team understands how variables such as temperature, moisture, and mix ratios influence the final result. Small adjustments during installation can significantly impact the durability of the finished surface.<br>\n<br>Working with a trusted <a href=\"https://share.google/AG4d5IyY1119AP3Qw\" class=\"text-primary\"><b><u>Nassau County construction company</u></b></a> ensures that these technical details are handled correctly. Professional builders evaluate soil conditions, drainage patterns, and structural requirements before beginning any work.<br>\n<br>ORA Construction has built its reputation by combining these technical skills with strong project management. As a respected home builder serving Syosset and surrounding areas, the company approaches every project with attention to detail and a commitment to lasting quality.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Create\n                        Website</a></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "venLhCMYcZ",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "article01-1j"
        },
        {
          "_name": "list03",
          "_sourceTheme": "promotionm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"list03 promotionm5\" group=\"List\" plugins=\"mbr-switch-arrow, mobirise-icons2\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icon\" name=\"showIcon\" checked condition=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <header>List</header>\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">4</option>\n            <option value=\"5\" selected>5</option>\n            <option value=\"6\">6</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Number\" name=\"showNumber\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"iconColor\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon BG\" value=\"#f3350c\" name=\"iconBg\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Active Color\" value=\"#1f1f1f\" name=\"activeColor\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Active BG\" value=\"#c6c6c6\" name=\"activeBg\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Border Color\" value=\"#c6c6c6\" name=\"border\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f1f1f1\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row content-wrap\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-3 card\">\n                            <div class=\"label-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\">\n                                <div class=\"label-wrap\">\n                                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"card-icon mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-shopping-basket mobi-mbri\" data-app-selector=\".card-icon\" style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); fill: rgb(31, 31, 31);\"></span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-label mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-label, .label-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Radiance\n                                    </p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-7 card\">\n                            <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper, .main-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                                    FAQs</h2>\n                            </div>\n                            <div id=\"bootstrap-accordion\" class=\"panel-group accordionStyles accordion\" role=\"tablist\" aria-multiselectable=\"true\">\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingOne\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse1\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    01\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">How long does a large residential construction project take?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Timelines vary depending on the project size. A full new home construction Long Island project may take 8–14 months, while renovations or additions may take several weeks to several months.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 1\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingTwo\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse2\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse2\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    02\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">What does a general contractor do during a residential project?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingTwo\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">A general contractor Nassau County manages the entire construction process. This includes scheduling trades, supervising work, coordinating materials, and ensuring compliance with local building regulations.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 2\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingThree\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse3\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    03\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">Why is concrete important in residential construction?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingThree\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Concrete provides the strong foundation required to support the structure of a home. Properly installed concrete foundations ensure long-term stability and durability.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 3\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingFour\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse4\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse4\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    04\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">Is finishing a basement a good investment?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingFour\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Yes. A professional basement remodel Long Island adds usable living space and can significantly increase a home’s overall value.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 4\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingFive\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse5\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse5\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    05\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">What should homeowners consider before starting a large renovation?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingFive\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Homeowners should evaluate their budget, timeline, and long-term goals. Working with an experienced construction company ensures that planning, design, and construction are handled professionally.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 5\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingSix\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse6\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse6\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    06\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n                                                    How do you support models’ careers long-term?\n                                                </h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse6\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingSix\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">\n                                                We offer mentoring, career planning, and access to industry connections,\n                                                helping models grow and maintain a successful career over time.\n                                            </p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".content-wrap": {
              "margin": "0 -50px",
              ".card": {
                "padding": "0 50px"
              },
              ".label-wrapper": {
                "margin-bottom": "20px",
                ".label-wrap": {
                  "display": "inline-flex",
                  "flex-wrap": "wrap",
                  "align-items": "center",
                  "gap": "8px",
                  ".iconfont-wrapper": {
                    "display": "flex",
                    ".mbr-iconfont": {
                      "display": "inline-flex",
                      "font-size": "20px"
                    }
                  },
                  ".mbr-label": {
                    "margin-bottom": "0"
                  }
                }
              },
              ".title-wrapper": {
                ".mbr-section-title": {
                  "margin-bottom": "50px"
                }
              }
            },
            ".panel-group": {
              ".card": {
                "position": "relative",
                "background-color": "transparent",
                "border-bottom": "1px solid @border",
                "border-radius": "0 !important",
                "padding": "30px 0",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "padding": "20px 0"
                },
                "&:first-child": {
                  "border-top": "1px solid @border"
                },
                ".card-header": {
                  "background-color": "transparent",
                  "border": "none",
                  "border-radius": "0",
                  "padding": "0",
                  ".panel-title": {
                    "display": "flex",
                    "justify-content": "space-between",
                    "align-items": "center",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "padding": "0",
                    ".title-wrap": {
                      "display": "flex",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "gap": "20px",
                      "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                        "display": "block"
                      },
                      ".panel-number": {
                        "margin-bottom": "0",
                        "white-space": "nowrap",
                        "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                          "margin-bottom": "20px",
                          "width": "0"
                        }
                      },
                      ".panel-title-edit": {
                        "margin-bottom": "0"
                      }
                    },
                    ".icon-wrapper": {
                      "width": "24px",
                      "height": "24px",
                      "min-width": "24px",
                      "display": "inline-flex",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "justify-content": "center",
                      "margin-left": "24px",
                      "transition": "all 0.3s ease-in-out",
                      "background-color": "@iconBg",
                      ".mbr-iconfont": {
                        "font-size": "10px",
                        "transition": "all 0.3s ease-in-out",
                        "color": "@iconColor"
                      }
                    },
                    "&:not(.collapsed)": {
                      ".icon-wrapper": {
                        "background-color": "@activeBg",
                        ".mbr-iconfont": {
                          "transform": "rotate(-45deg)",
                          "color": "@activeColor"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                ".panel-collapse": {
                  ".panel-body": {
                    "padding": "20px 44px 0 44px",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "padding": "20px 0 0 0"
                    },
                    ".panel-text": {
                      "margin-bottom": "0"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-label": {
              "color": "#1f1f1f"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#1f1f1f"
            },
            ".panel-number": {
              "color": "#1f1f1f"
            },
            ".panel-title-edit": {
              "color": "#1f1f1f"
            },
            ".item-text": {
              "color": "#5a5a5a"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "venLhDdSQm",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "list03-1k"
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".google-map": {
              "height": "35rem",
              "position": "relative",
              "iframe": {
                "height": "100%",
                "width": "100%",
                "border-radius": "2rem"
              },
              "[data-state-details]": {
                "color": "#6b6763",
                "height": "1.5em",
                "margin-top": "-0.75em",
                "padding-left": "1.25rem",
                "padding-right": "1.25rem",
                "position": "absolute",
                "text-align": "center",
                "top": "50%",
                "width": "100%"
              },
              "&[data-state]": {
                "background": "#e9e5dc"
              },
              "&[data-state=\"loading\"]": {
                "[data-state-details]": {
                  "display": "none"
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            }
          },
          "_name": "map01",
          "_sourceTheme": "discretem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"map1\" group=\"Maps\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"fullWidth\" title=\"Full Width\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Map</header>\n        <input type=\"map\" title=\"Map\" name=\"googleMap\" place-id=\"<iframe src=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3188.7878633363084!2d-73.5098697!3d40.812250399999996!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c281751430800f%3A0x8b31bcceb8203724!2sOra%20Construction%20-%20Home%20Remodeling%2C%20Masonry%20%26%20Landscape%20Design!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sro!4v1773819835510!5m2!1sen!2sro&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; style=&quot;border:0;&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer-when-downgrade&quot;></iframe>\" value=\"<iframe src=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3188.7878633363084!2d-73.5098697!3d40.812250399999996!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c281751430800f%3A0x8b31bcceb8203724!2sOra%20Construction%20-%20Home%20Remodeling%2C%20Masonry%20%26%20Landscape%20Design!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sro!4v1773819835510!5m2!1sen!2sro&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; style=&quot;border:0;&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer-when-downgrade&quot;></iframe>\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@THEME_PATH@/components/_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#04492e\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@THEME_PATH@/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-head mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n                <b>Visit Us</b>\n            </h3>\n            <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                Find us here\n            </h4>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"google-map\" mbr-map=\"googleMap\">\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "venLhDLyaw",
