          "_name": "article02",
          "_sourceTheme": "launchm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article02 launchm5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow 1\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"cardShadow_1\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow 2\" value=\"#cccccc\" name=\"cardShadow_2\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Container BG\" value=\"#fafafa\" name=\"cardBg\">\n        <header>Border</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Border\" name=\"showBorder\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#e1e7ed\" name=\"border\" condition=\"showBorder\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/launchm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f5f5f5\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/launchm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#f5f5f5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"border-wrap border_1\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"border-wrap border_2\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                        <div class=\"row items-wrapper\">\n                            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 card\">\n                                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Masonry Materials For Outdoor Living Spaces</b></h2>\n                                    <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrapper\">Outdoor living areas have become a major focus in modern residential construction. Homeowners increasingly want patios, decks, and gathering spaces that extend their living area beyond the interior of the home. Masonry materials play a crucial role in making these spaces both beautiful and durable.<br>\n<br>A patio and deck builder Syosset residents rely on will often incorporate brick, stone, or concrete pavers into outdoor designs. These materials can withstand weather exposure while maintaining visual appeal. They also create stable surfaces for seating areas, fire pits, and walkways that connect different parts of the property.<br>\n<br>These features are often part of larger construction projects managed by a home addition contractor Long Island homeowners hire to expand their living space. When properly designed and installed, masonry elements help outdoor spaces blend seamlessly with the architecture of the home while adding long-term value to the property.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Get Started\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 card\">\n                                <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                                    <img class=\"little-radius\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/25.webp\" alt>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "venUoZhV8g",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "article02-1z"
        },
        {
          "_name": "tabs01",
          "_sourceTheme": "standm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"tabs01 tabs standm5\" group=\"List\" plugins=\"mbr-tabs\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Tabs</header>\n        <select title=\"Count\" name=\"bootstrapTabs\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"4\" selected>4</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"tabs\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG\" value=\"#000000\" name=\"tabsBg\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Active Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"activeColor\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Active BG\" value=\"#e70000\" name=\"activeBg\" selected>\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Date\" name=\"showDate\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG 1\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"cardBg_1\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG 2\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" name=\"cardBg_2\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow\" value=\"#6c7179\" name=\"shadow\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/standm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/standm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12\">\n                            <div class=\"tabs-wrapper\">\n                                <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\" role=\"tablist\">\n                                    <li mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"nav-item first mbr-fonts-style\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd,-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-iconFont\"><a class=\"nav-link show mbr-fonts-style little-radius active\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tabs01-5_tab0\" aria-selected=\"true\">\n                                            310 Harbor Rd, Cold Spring Harbor, NY 11724, USA\n                                        </a></li>\n                                    <li mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"nav-item\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 1\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd,-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-iconFont\"><a class=\"nav-link mbr-fonts-style little-radius active\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tabs01-5_tab1\" aria-selected=\"true\">\n                                            2500 6th St, East Meadow, NY 11554, USA\n                                        </a></li>\n                                    <li mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"nav-item\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 2\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd,-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-iconFont\"><a class=\"nav-link mbr-fonts-style little-radius active\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tabs01-5_tab2\" aria-selected=\"true\">\n                                            1135 Walt Whitman Rd, Melville, NY 11747, USA\n                                        </a></li>\n                                    <li mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"nav-item\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 3\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd,-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-iconFont\"><a class=\"nav-link mbr-fonts-style little-radius active\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" role=\"tab\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tabs01-5_tab3\" aria-selected=\"true\">\n                                            8 Woodhollow Ln, Huntington, NY 11743, USA\n                                        </a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"tab-content\">\n                                <div id=\"tab1\" class=\"tab-pane in active\" role=\"tabpanel\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-wrapper large-radius\">\n                                        <div class=\"card-box card-wrap\">\n                                            <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .tabs-wrapper, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"></h4>\n                                            <p class=\"item-date mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-date\" mbr-if=\"showDate\">\n                                                March 12, 2030\n                                            </p>\n                                            <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\"></p>\n                                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-iconFont\">\n                                                <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    See More\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                                            <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1P1gqkrjFVFunGV4oklU6nsBdTIJSqzA&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div id=\"tab2\" class=\"tab-pane\" role=\"tabpanel\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 1\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-wrapper large-radius\">\n                                        <div class=\"card-box card-wrap\">\n                                            <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .tabs-wrapper, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"></h4>\n                                            <p class=\"item-date mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-date\" mbr-if=\"showDate\">\n                                                June 20, 2030\n                                            </p>\n                                            <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\"></p>\n                                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-iconFont\">\n                                                <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    See More\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                                            <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1voJ75HQHMONUPVPGUWGny8ruYljLVyM&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div id=\"tab3\" class=\"tab-pane\" role=\"tabpanel\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 2\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-wrapper large-radius\">\n                                        <div class=\"card-box card-wrap\">\n                                            <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .tabs-wrapper, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"></h4>\n                                            <p class=\"item-date mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-date\" mbr-if=\"showDate\">\n                                                September 5, 2030\n                                            </p>\n                                            <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\"></p>\n                                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-iconFont\">\n                                                <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    See More\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                                            <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=152Mfe7T5dcVkRr3SypEGl2Tr7zda5dg&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div id=\"tab4\" class=\"tab-pane\" role=\"tabpanel\" mbr-if=\"bootstrapTabs > 3\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-wrapper large-radius\">\n                                        <div class=\"card-box card-wrap\">\n                                            <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .tabs-wrapper, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">500 Searingtown Rd, Roslyn, NY 11576, USA</h4>\n                                            <p class=\"item-date mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-date\" mbr-if=\"showDate\">\n                                                December 3, 2030\n                                            </p>\n                                            <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1C4jHvOnIbmM-uxI4MNV1XYXa_nqaqaw&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe></p>\n                                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-iconFont\">\n                                                <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    See More\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                                            <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1w19kpBDC2pgpWbHuXjA1dCHc1QwNZI4&ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".tabs-wrapper": {
              "margin-bottom": "40px",
              ".nav.nav-tabs": {
                "border": "none",
                "padding": "0",
                "border-radius": "0 !important",
                "background-color": "transparent",
                "display": "inline-flex",
                "flex-wrap": "wrap",
                "gap": "12px",
                ".nav-item": {
                  "padding": "0",
                  "border": "none",
                  "display": "block",
                  "margin": "0",
                  ".nav-link": {
                    "position": "relative",
                    "display": "flex",
                    "align-items": "center",
                    "justify-content": "center",
                    "color": "@tabs",
                    "padding": "17px 24px",
                    "background-color": "@tabsBg",
                    "border": "none",
                    "transition": "background-color 1s ease-in-out",
                    "z-index": "1",
                    "overflow": "hidden",
                    "&::after": {
                      "content": "''",
                      "width": "12px",
                      "height": "12px",
                      "border-radius": "100%",
                      "transition": "all .8s ease",
                      "z-index": "-1",
                      "transform": "scale(1)",
                      "background-color": "@activeBg",
                      "margin-left": "16px",
                      "pointer-events": "none"
                    },
                    "&::before": {
                      "content": "''",
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "right": "24px",
                      "width": "12px",
                      "height": "12px",
                      "border-radius": "100%",
                      "transition": "all .8s ease",
                      "z-index": "1",
                      "opacity": "0",
                      "pointer-events": "none",
                      "background-color": "@activeColor"
                    },
                    "&:hover": {
                      "&::after": {
                        "transform": "scale(1.3)"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  ".nav-link.active": {
                    "color": "@activeColor",
                    "background-color": "@activeBg",
                    "&::after": {
                      "transform": "scale(50)"
                    },
                    "&::before": {
                      "opacity": "1"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".tab-content": {
              ".tab-pane": {
                ".card-wrapper": {
                  "display": "grid",
                  "grid-template-columns": "1fr 1fr",
                  "gap": "8px",
                  "background-color": "@cardBg_1",
                  "padding": "8px",
                  "box-shadow": "0 10px 25px -20px @shadow",
                  "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                    "grid-template-columns": "1fr"
                  },
                  ".card-box": {
                    "padding": "24px",
                    "background-color": "@cardBg_2",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "padding": "20px"
                    },
                    ".item-title": {
                      "margin-bottom": "12px"
                    },
                    ".item-date": {
                      "margin-bottom": "20px"
                    },
                    ".item-text": {
                      "margin-bottom": "0"
                    },
                    ".mbr-section-btn": {
                      "margin-top": "12px",
                      ".btn": {
                        "margin-bottom": "0"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  ".image-wrap": {
                    "position": "relative",
                    "min-height": "420px",
                    "height": "100%",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "height": "300px",
                      "min-height": "auto"
                    },
                    "img": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "top": "0",
                      "left": "0",
                      "width": "100%",
                      "height": "100%",
                      "object-fit": "cover"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".item-title": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".item-date": {
              "color": "#454545"
            },
            ".item-text": {
              "color": "#6c7179"
            }
          },
          "_PHPplaceholders": [],
          "_JSplaceholders": [],
          "_cid": "venUoZJTtJ",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "tabs01-20"
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "background": "white",
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "width": "fit-content",
              "border-radius": "2rem",
              "padding": "5px 1rem",
              "text-align": "left"
            },
            ".subtitle-wrap": {
              "display": "inline-flex",
              "border-radius": "2rem",
              "padding": "0.5rem",
              "padding-bottom": "0",
              "background": "@primaryColor",
              "flex-direction": "row",
              "width": "fit-content",
              "align-items": "center",
              "margin-bottom": "2rem",
              ".mbr-iconfont": {
                "padding": "0 15px",
                "padding-bottom": "8px",
                "margin": "0",
                "color": "@secondaryColor",
                "font-size": "1.5rem"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#04492e"
            },
            ".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle, .align-wrapper": {
              "color": "#04492e",
              "text-align": "center"
            }
          },
          "_name": "article01",
          "_sourceTheme": "discretem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article1\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\n        <input type=\"range\" inline name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"9\" step=\"1\">\n        <select title=\"Align\" name=\"contentAlign\">\n            <option value selected>Left</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-center\">Center</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-end\">Right</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#fafaf9\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#fafafa\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.1\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div class mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row  align-left {{contentAlign}}\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"align-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showSubitle\">\n                    <div class=\"subtitle-wrap\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-idea mobi-mbri\" style=\"color: rgb(219, 180, 13); fill: rgb(219, 180, 13);\"></span>\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle, .align-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubitle\"><b>Choosing The Right Masonry Material For Home Remodeling</b></h2>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>How to Manage <br>Your Business</b></h1>\n\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Selecting the best masonry material requires careful consideration of both structural needs and design goals. During projects such as a basement remodel Long Island homes often require reinforced walls, moisture protection, and durable flooring materials. Concrete and masonry blocks frequently provide the stability needed for these environments.<br>\n<br>For exterior projects, homeowners may choose brick or stone to match existing architecture while enhancing curb appeal. An experienced home builder or construction professional will evaluate each project individually, ensuring that materials align with both structural requirements and aesthetic preferences.<br>\n<br>Working with a trusted <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/?cid=10030005441169209124\" class=\"text-primary\"><b><u>general contractor Nassau County</u></b></a> homeowners respect ensures that every phase of construction—from design planning to material selection—is handled with expertise. Professionals understand how to combine masonry materials effectively, creating structures that are not only strong but also visually appealing.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Create\n                        Website</a></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "venUp0pFuO",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "article01-21"
        },
        {
          "_name": "list03",
          "_sourceTheme": "promotionm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"list03 promotionm5\" group=\"List\" plugins=\"mbr-switch-arrow, mobirise-icons2\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icon\" name=\"showIcon\" checked condition=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <header>List</header>\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">4</option>\n            <option value=\"5\" selected>5</option>\n            <option value=\"6\">6</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Number\" name=\"showNumber\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"iconColor\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon BG\" value=\"#f3350c\" name=\"iconBg\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Active Color\" value=\"#1f1f1f\" name=\"activeColor\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Active BG\" value=\"#c6c6c6\" name=\"activeBg\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Border Color\" value=\"#c6c6c6\" name=\"border\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f1f1f1\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row content-wrap\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-3 card\">\n                            <div class=\"label-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\">\n                                <div class=\"label-wrap\">\n                                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"card-icon mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-shopping-basket mobi-mbri\" data-app-selector=\".card-icon\" style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); fill: rgb(31, 31, 31);\"></span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-label mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-label, .label-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Radiance\n                                    </p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-7 card\">\n                            <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper, .main-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                                    FAQs</h2>\n                            </div>\n                            <div id=\"bootstrap-accordion\" class=\"panel-group accordionStyles accordion\" role=\"tablist\" aria-multiselectable=\"true\">\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingOne\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse1\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    01\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">What is masonry in construction?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Masonry is a building technique that uses materials such as brick, stone, and concrete bonded together with mortar to create durable walls, foundations, and structural elements.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 1\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingTwo\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse2\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse2\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    02\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">Why does masonry improve structural strength?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingTwo\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Masonry distributes structural weight evenly and provides excellent load-bearing support. This helps buildings resist cracking, shifting, and long-term structural damage.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 2\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingThree\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse3\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    03\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">How long does masonry construction last?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingThree\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">When installed correctly by experienced professionals, masonry structures can last several decades or even centuries with minimal maintenance.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 3\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingFour\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse4\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse4\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    04\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">Is masonry used in home renovation projects?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingFour\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Yes. Masonry is often used in projects like home remodeling Long Island, structural reinforcement, foundation repair, and basement renovations.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 4\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingFive\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse5\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse5\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    05\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">Does masonry increase property value?</h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingFive\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Yes. Durable features such as strong foundations, concrete driveways, and professionally installed masonry walls can increase property value and improve long-term durability.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card little-radius\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 5\">\n                                    <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingSix\">\n                                        <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse6\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse6\">\n                                            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-number\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\">\n                                                    06\n                                                </h4>\n                                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n                                                    How do you support models’ careers long-term?\n                                                </h4>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"icon-wrapper card-wrap little-radius\">\n                                                <span class=\"sign mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-plus mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"collapse6\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingSix\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                                        <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                            <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">\n                                                We offer mentoring, career planning, and access to industry connections,\n                                                helping models grow and maintain a successful career over time.\n                                            </p>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".content-wrap": {
              "margin": "0 -50px",
              ".card": {
                "padding": "0 50px"
              },
              ".label-wrapper": {
                "margin-bottom": "20px",
                ".label-wrap": {
                  "display": "inline-flex",
                  "flex-wrap": "wrap",
                  "align-items": "center",
                  "gap": "8px",
                  ".iconfont-wrapper": {
                    "display": "flex",
                    ".mbr-iconfont": {
                      "display": "inline-flex",
                      "font-size": "20px"
                    }
                  },
                  ".mbr-label": {
                    "margin-bottom": "0"
                  }
                }
              },
              ".title-wrapper": {
                ".mbr-section-title": {
                  "margin-bottom": "50px"
                }
              }
            },
            ".panel-group": {
              ".card": {
                "position": "relative",
                "background-color": "transparent",
                "border-bottom": "1px solid @border",
                "border-radius": "0 !important",
                "padding": "30px 0",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "padding": "20px 0"
                },
                "&:first-child": {
                  "border-top": "1px solid @border"
                },
                ".card-header": {
                  "background-color": "transparent",
                  "border": "none",
                  "border-radius": "0",
                  "padding": "0",
                  ".panel-title": {
                    "display": "flex",
                    "justify-content": "space-between",
                    "align-items": "center",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "padding": "0",
                    ".title-wrap": {
                      "display": "flex",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "gap": "20px",
                      "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                        "display": "block"
                      },
                      ".panel-number": {
                        "margin-bottom": "0",
                        "white-space": "nowrap",
                        "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                          "margin-bottom": "20px",
                          "width": "0"
                        }
                      },
                      ".panel-title-edit": {
                        "margin-bottom": "0"
                      }
                    },
                    ".icon-wrapper": {
                      "width": "24px",
                      "height": "24px",
                      "min-width": "24px",
                      "display": "inline-flex",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "justify-content": "center",
                      "margin-left": "24px",
                      "transition": "all 0.3s ease-in-out",
                      "background-color": "@iconBg",
                      ".mbr-iconfont": {
                        "font-size": "10px",
                        "transition": "all 0.3s ease-in-out",
                        "color": "@iconColor"
                      }
                    },
                    "&:not(.collapsed)": {
                      ".icon-wrapper": {
                        "background-color": "@activeBg",
                        ".mbr-iconfont": {
                          "transform": "rotate(-45deg)",
                          "color": "@activeColor"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                ".panel-collapse": {
                  ".panel-body": {
                    "padding": "20px 44px 0 44px",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "padding": "20px 0 0 0"
                    },
                    ".panel-text": {
                      "margin-bottom": "0"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-label": {
              "color": "#1f1f1f"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#1f1f1f"
            },
            ".panel-number": {
              "color": "#1f1f1f"
            },
            ".panel-title-edit": {
              "color": "#1f1f1f"
            },
            ".item-text": {
              "color": "#5a5a5a"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "venUp0Zx0h",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "list03-22"
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".google-map": {
              "height": "35rem",
              "position": "relative",
              "iframe": {
                "height": "100%",
                "width": "100%",
                "border-radius": "2rem"
              },
              "[data-state-details]": {
                "color": "#6b6763",
                "height": "1.5em",
                "margin-top": "-0.75em",
                "padding-left": "1.25rem",
                "padding-right": "1.25rem",
                "position": "absolute",
                "text-align": "center",
                "top": "50%",
                "width": "100%"
              },
              "&[data-state]": {
                "background": "#e9e5dc"
              },
              "&[data-state=\"loading\"]": {
                "[data-state-details]": {
                  "display": "none"
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            }
          },
          "_name": "map01",
          "_sourceTheme": "discretem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"map1\" group=\"Maps\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"fullWidth\" title=\"Full Width\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Map</header>\n        <input type=\"map\" title=\"Map\" name=\"googleMap\" place-id=\"<iframe src=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3188.7878633363084!2d-73.5098697!3d40.812250399999996!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c281751430800f%3A0x8b31bcceb8203724!2sOra%20Construction%20-%20Home%20Remodeling%2C%20Masonry%20%26%20Landscape%20Design!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sro!4v1773819835510!5m2!1sen!2sro&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; style=&quot;border:0;&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer-when-downgrade&quot;></iframe>\" value=\"<iframe src=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3188.7878633363084!2d-73.5098697!3d40.812250399999996!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c281751430800f%3A0x8b31bcceb8203724!2sOra%20Construction%20-%20Home%20Remodeling%2C%20Masonry%20%26%20Landscape%20Design!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sro!4v1773819835510!5m2!1sen!2sro&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; style=&quot;border:0;&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer-when-downgrade&quot;></iframe>\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@THEME_PATH@/components/_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#04492e\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@THEME_PATH@/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-head mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n                <b>Visit Us</b>\n            </h3>\n            <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                Find us here\n            </h4>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"google-map\" mbr-map=\"googleMap\">\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "venUp1Beyw",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "map01-23"
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value",
              "& when (@showGradientBg)": {
                "background-image": "linear-gradient(180deg, @gradientColor_1 0%, @bg-value 100%)"
              }
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".title-wrapper": {
              "margin-bottom": "50px",
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "40px"
              },
              ".mbr-label": {
                "margin-bottom": "30px"
              },
              ".mbr-section-title": {
                "margin-bottom": "0"
              },
              ".mbr-text": {
                "margin-top": "20px",
                "margin-bottom": "0"
              },
              ".mbr-section-btn": {
                "margin-top": "20px",
                "margin-bottom": "-9.6px"
              }
            },
            ".nav-wrapper": {
              "display": "flex",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "flex-wrap": "wrap",
              "gap": "30px 0",
              "margin-bottom": "50px",
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "40px"
              },
              ".nav-wrap": {
                "padding-left": "20px",
                "width": "25%",
                "@media (max-width: 1440px)": {
                  "padding-left": "0",
                  "width": "50%"
                },
                "@media (max-width: 768px)": {
                  "width": "100%"
                },
                "&:first-child": {
                  "padding-left": "0"
                },
                "&:nth-child(3n)": {
                  "@media (max-width: 1440px)": {
                    "padding-left": "0"
                  }
                },
                ".mbr-list-title": {
                  "margin-bottom": "20px",
                  "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                    "margin-bottom": "16px"
                  }
                },
                ".list": {
                  "padding": "0",
                  "margin": "0",
                  "list-style-type": "none",
                  ".item-wrap": {
                    "margin-bottom": "16px",
                    "transition": "all 0.3s ease-in-out",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "margin-bottom": "10px"
                    },
                    "&:hover, &:focus": {
                      "opacity": "0.7"
                    },
                    "&:last-child": {
                      "margin-bottom": "0"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".border-wrap": {
              "margin-bottom": "50px",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "1px",
              "opacity": ".4",
              "background-color": "@border",
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "40px"
              }
            },
            ".card": {
              "justify-content": "center"
            },
            ".mbr-copy": {
              "margin-bottom": "0",
              "opacity": ".7",
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".social-wrapper": {
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "40px",
                "text-align": "left"
              },
              ".social-wrap": {
                "display": "inline-flex",
                "justify-content": "flex-end",
                "flex-wrap": "wrap",
                "gap": "30px",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "justify-content": "flex-start"
                },
                ".soc-item": {
                  "display": "inline-flex",
                  "align-items": "center",
                  "justify-content": "center",
                  "width": "25px",
                  "height": "25px",
                  "transition": "all .3s ease",
                  "&:hover, &:hover": {
                    "opacity": ".7",
                    "a.mbr-iconfont": {
                      "opacity": ".7"
                    }
                  },
                  "a": {
                    "position": "relative",
                    "z-index": "1",
                    "display": "block",
                    ".mbr-iconfont": {
                      "display": "block",
                      "font-size": "25px",
                      "transition": "all 0.3s ease-in-out"
                    }
                  }
                }
              },
              "text-align": "right"
            },
            ".mbr-label": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-list-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".list": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            }
          },
          "_name": "footer01",
          "_sourceTheme": "integrationm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"footer01 integrationm5\" group=\"Footer\" global once=\"footers\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Navigation\" name=\"showNav\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Navigation Title\" name=\"showNavTitle\" condition=\"showNav\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Navigation Amount\" name=\"listAmount\" min=\"1\" max=\"4\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" condition=\"showNav\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Social\" name=\"showSocial\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Amount\" name=\"soc\" min=\"1\" max=\"3\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\" condition=\"showSocial\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Border\" name=\"showBorder\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Border Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"border\" condition=\"showBorder\" selected>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Copyright\" name=\"showCopy\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/integrationm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#171719\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/integrationm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <header condition=\"bg.type == 'color'\">Gradient</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Gradient\" name=\"showGradientBg\" condition=\"bg.type == 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Gradient Color\" value=\"#04492e\" name=\"gradientColor_1\" condition=\"showGradientBg && bg.type == 'color'\" selected>\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-11\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\" mbr-if=\"showLabel || showTitle || showText || showButtons\">\n                            <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                                <p class=\"mbr-label card-wrap mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-label\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/?cid=10030005441169209124\" class=\"text-primary\">Ora Construction - Home Remodeling, Masonry &amp; Landscape Design</a></p>\n                                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn, .title-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b><a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-primary\">home remodeling Long Island</a></b></h2>\n                                <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrapper\">\n                                        Business Directory is a trusted platform designed to connect companies,\n                                        professionals, and service providers in one place.\n                                    </p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-white\" href=\"privacy-policy.html\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><strong>Privacy Policy</strong></a></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\" mbr-if=\"showNav\">\n                            <div class=\"nav-wrapper\">\n                                <div class=\"nav-wrap\">\n                                    <h4 class=\"mbr-list-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-list-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showNavTitle\">\n                                        <b>Menu</b>\n                                    </h4>\n                                    <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".list, .item-wrap\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                                        <li class=\"item-wrap\">Address</li>\n                                    </ul>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"nav-wrap\" mbr-if=\"listAmount > 1\">\n                                    <h4 class=\"mbr-list-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-list-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showNavTitle\">\n                                        <b>Features</b>\n                                    </h4>\n                                    <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".list, .item-wrap\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                                        <li class=\"item-wrap\">Useful Links</li>\n                                    </ul>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"nav-wrap\" mbr-if=\"listAmount > 2\">\n                                    <h4 class=\"mbr-list-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-list-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showNavTitle\">\n                                        <b>Clients</b>\n                                    </h4>\n                                    <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".list, .item-wrap\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                                        <li class=\"item-wrap\">Ora Construction - Home Remodeling, Masonry &amp; Landscape Design\n</li><li class=\"item-wrap\">24 David Drive, Syosset,\n</li><li class=\"item-wrap\">NY 11791\n</li><li class=\"item-wrap\"><b><u>Phone Number:\n</u></b></li><li class=\"item-wrap\">(516) 697-7680</li><li class=\"item-wrap\">\n</li>\n                                    </ul>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"nav-wrap\" mbr-if=\"listAmount > 3\">\n                                    <h4 class=\"mbr-list-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-list-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showNavTitle\">\n                                        <b>Team</b>\n                                    </h4>\n                                    <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".list, .item-wrap\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                                        <li class=\"item-wrap\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=Syosset%2C+NY\" class=\"text-primary\">Syosset, NY</a>\n</li><li class=\"item-wrap\"><a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/p2RHU3FSxtJUNaCX7\" class=\"text-primary\">The Great Escape Room Long Island</a>\n</li><li class=\"item-wrap\"><a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/MjJuVqKy6fffbhBa9\" class=\"text-primary\">Bounce! Family Entertainment Center</a>\n</li><li class=\"item-wrap\"><a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/NcaPKYrhZz1jBXca6\" class=\"text-primary\">AMF Syosset Lanes</a></li>\n                                    </ul>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12\">\n                            <div class=\"border-wrap\" mbr-if=\"showBorder\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"row justify-content-center flex-row-reverse\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 card\" mbr-if=\"showSocial\">\n                            <div class=\"social-wrapper\">\n                                <div class=\"social-wrap\">\n                                    <div class=\"soc-item\">\n                                        <a href=\"https://mobiri.se/\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont card-icon socicon socicon-facebook\" data-app-selector=\".card-icon\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); fill: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"soc-item\" mbr-if=\"soc > 1\">\n                                        <a href=\"https://mobiri.se/\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon socicon-instagram\" data-app-selector=\".card-icon\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); fill: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"soc-item\" mbr-if=\"soc > 2\">\n                                        <a href=\"https://mobiri.se/\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon socicon-linkedin\" data-app-selector=\".card-icon\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); fill: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 card\">\n                            <p class=\"mbr-copy mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-copy\" mbr-if=\"showCopy\">\n                                © Copyright 2026 - All Rights Reserved\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "venUp2a3FH",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": true,
          "_once": "footers",
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "footer01-24"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}